T00:49:09.000Z","msg":"本身咁靚，靠化妝都做到啦，駛乜整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09d94ba2797bf7633b2eee6b16469b7760097070","tid":2390491,"uid":52358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T04:49:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b93b0df6e6b184918232740a369ff54413ffcf18","tid":2390491,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0bed035f98b76dcc0fe75bdfd1f83e9fb7e95267","tid":2390491,"uid":178453,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T15:06:52.000Z","msg":"整完無左種凡人既感覺<br />\n變左倒模整容樣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T05:07:05.000Z","msg":"sims 4 膠樣"},{"pid":"1d554ca08ca4f9ce66ac5dac511dcc81c9c6d20a","tid":2390491,"uid":80724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T06:21:55.000Z","msg":"所以你話點解呢個世界咁多女人咁on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明本身都底都靚，但就走去搞埋啲咁嘅嘢<br />\n最後都唔知似乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}